        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Not Providing 6 Months Income History</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600">You need 6 months of documented income—not 3 months like some other countries. Bank statements or payslips for the full 6-month period preceding your application are required.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-red-500 pl-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Missing Medical Certificate</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600">Romania requires a medical certificate showing you're in good health. Some applicants overlook this. Get a recent medical exam from a licensed physician before applying.</p>
